author: jeremias
msg: Fixed some sources of "wrong operand type" error in Acrobat Reader.
They were caused by rounding bugs, mostly experienced with SVG files coming from OpenOffice.
The PDF contained matrices like "0 0 0 0 0 0 cm" when the values really shouldn't be zero.
